# Environment Variables for Local Development

# ========================================
# COST-OPTIMIZED MULTI-MODEL ARCHITECTURE
# ========================================

# Cheap model for outfit analysis (Gemini 1.5 Flash - text only)
# This model is ~4x cheaper than image model
# Used by: /api/describe
DESCRIBE_GATEWAY_URL=https://gateway.ai.cloudflare.com/v1/{account_id}/virtry-gateway/google-ai-studio/v1beta/models/gemini-1.5-flash:generateContent

# Expensive model for image generation (Gemini 2.5 Flash IMAGE)
# Used by: /api/generate
GENERATE_GATEWAY_URL=https://gateway.ai.cloudflare.com/v1/{account_id}/virtry-gateway/google-ai-studio/v1beta/models/gemini-2.5-flash-image:generateContent

# Shared Gateway token for both models
GATEWAY_TOKEN=cf_xxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ========================================
# LEGACY (for backward compatibility)
# ========================================

# If DESCRIBE_GATEWAY_URL is not set, falls back to GATEWAY_URL
GATEWAY_URL=https://gateway.ai.cloudflare.com/v1/{account_id}/virtry-gateway/google-ai-studio/v1beta/models/gemini-2.5-flash-image:generateContent

# ========================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ========================================
#
# 1. Go to https://dash.cloudflare.com/
# 2. Navigate to AI → AI Gateway
# 3. Create a new Gateway named "virtry-gateway"
# 4. Create TWO routes in the Gateway:
#    a) Route for gemini-1.5-flash (cheap text model)
#    b) Route for gemini-2.5-flash-image (expensive image model)
# 5. Copy the URLs and paste above (replace {account_id})
# 6. Go to AI → Manage → Create API Token
# 7. Set permissions: AI:Read + AI:Edit
# 8. Copy the token and paste above (cf_xxxxxxxxxxxxx)
#
# For more details, see:
# - GATEWAY_SETUP.md
# - COST_OPTIMIZATION.md
